2017", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC8162.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document describes how to use secure DNS to associate an S/MIME user's certificate with the intended domain name, similar to the way that DNS-Based Authentication of Named Entities (DANE), RFC 6698, does for TLS."];
